summary:
InspiringFifty TopFifty Deep Tech (2021) • International Venture Club Healthcare Subgroup Lead (2017)• Global Corporate Venturing Rising Star (2015)• Corporate Entrepreneur of the Year (2010)

Dynamic leader with 20 years of strategic healthcare experience in new ventures and investments across HealthTech & MedTech, and Finance Solutions for Global Public Health. Passionate about sustainable finance, impact capital, and building new ventures.   

Board Member• Venture Partner 

New Business Development and Innovation Leader • New Venture Creation and Execution • Impact Investment Strategies •  Informatics and Digital  • External Alliances and Partnerships • Post- Acquisition Integration• Drug Device Combination Technologies and Solutions • Supply Chain Innovation• Real World Data Platforms • Global Public Health • Prevention & Nutrition •

MBA in Entrepreneurship, Babson College, USA 2010• 
Post Graduate Degree in Global Business, University of Oxford, UK 2012
